Package: tif2gif
Type: Package
Title: TIF to GIF
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lauren Harris
Maintainer: Lauren Harris <lnharris@ucsb.edu>
Description: This package contains a function which acts as a wrapper for tmap's animation function. This wrapper makes it easier to import specific files from mixed contents folders. It also makes it easier to generate more than one GIF at a time (using pmap). 
License: NA
Encoding: UTF-8
